 193:../../Middlewares/LVGL/GUI/lvgl/src/widgets/roller/lv_roller.c ****     /*Set the value even if it's the same as the current value because
 194:../../Middlewares/LVGL/GUI/lvgl/src/widgets/roller/lv_roller.c ****      *if moving to the next option with an animation which was just deleted in the PRESS Call the a
 195:../../Middlewares/LVGL/GUI/lvgl/src/widgets/roller/lv_roller.c ****      *nothing will continue the animation.*/
 196:../../Middlewares/LVGL/GUI/lvgl/src/widgets/roller/lv_roller.c **** 
